          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-08-21T14:53:49Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Restoring Access, Improving Service to Enable Veterans Engaging To Fundraise Act of 2018 or the RAISE VET FUND Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the U.S. Postal Service to allow veterans service organizations (VSOs) that are recognized by the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to solicit donations by distributing items that are veterans symbols at a post office on the two business days before and after a federal holiday or Flag Day. VA-recognized VSOs include certain service organizations that are congressionally chartered and those that are not.</p> </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-07-10T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
